  "texts": [
    "But the broader umbrella of design alternative focuses on change, agency, difference, and the worldtransformative capacities of every meaning-maker (Cope and Kalantzis 2023e, Kalantzis et al.",
    "2016, New London Group 1996).The significance of Generative AI is that until now, only humans could do design in this definition.",
    "But now... For the first time in human history, a machine can design and communicate written-textual meanings (and, derivatively, image, speech and other forms of meaning) that have never been created before but are nevertheless coherent and meaningful to humans.The last one hundred words in this text, the last one hundred words you spoke, and the last one hundred words any three-year old child has spoken-have never been written or spoken quite this way before.",
    "Design is the capacity to create originally and distinctively voiced meanings from the infinite combinatorial possibilities in our available resources for meaning.",
    "Generative AI is the first machine that can do this too-though as we will shortly argue, it does this in ways so incomparably different from humans that it can hardly be classed an \"intellect."
  ],
